					<h1>The Ultimate Guide to Modern Web Development</h1>
					
					<p>Web development is evolving rapidly. Whether you are building static sites or dynamic applications, understanding the core fundamentals is crucial for long-term success in the digital industry.</p>

					<img src="https://picsum.photos/id/101/720/420" alt="Modern web development setup">

					<h2>Getting Started with Frameworks</h2>
					<p>Frameworks allow developers to build robust applications much faster. For instance, using a static site generator like <strong>Hugo</strong> can significantly improve your site's performance and security.</p>

					<h3>Why Performance Matters</h3>
					<p>Performance is not just about speed; it is about user experience. Search engines prioritize websites that load quickly and provide a seamless navigation flow for the user.</p>

					<blockquote>
						"Code is like humor. When you have to explain it, it’s bad." — Cory House
