					<h2>Implementing Your First Function</h2>
					<p>To get started, you can write a simple function. Below is an example of a JavaScript snippet that logs a message to your console:</p>

	<pre>
	<code>
		function greet(name) {
			console.log("Hello, " + name + "! Welcome to web development.");
		}
		greet("Developer");
	</code>
	</pre>

